{
  "stem": "945.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I came out of my typhus, I heard that he died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was the first one from our family and my favorite uncle, and I could not accept the fact that he died.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I couldn't deal with it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But no sooner I could crawl or walk, I went over to where I knew he lived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I found my aunt, and my cousins, and some other distant relatives in that little room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were all sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were all dying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My uncle died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They took his corpse away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But all the other corpses-- it was in the middle of winter-- they piled all those people in a large pile by another old synagogue that was there for hundreds of years.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They said from the time of the Turks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I walked into their house I asked my aunt what I could do, what they would like, and what can I do to help them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I found an old pair of my uncle shoes, and I went to the market and bartered it for a little bit of milk and whatever I could.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I brought that to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I left it with them and I crawled back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say crawled because I could hardly walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could make three, four steps, and then I would have to sit down and crawl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how I got back to our home or our place where we lived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The winter was very, very cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of people were naked, freezing to death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They simply bartered away everything they had, and they had nothing left for themselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of the people were, including myself and our family, make clothes out of old sacks, potato sacks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what we wore.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
